race.comment: DEEP STEALTH (3) is another winning chance for the local Matt Dunn yard. Has gone close all preparation and has been heavily bet at her last three. Maps for the run-of-the-race and has Newman's 1.5kg claim today. Deserves another chance. MATERIALIST (2) resumes and has placed 2/3 fresh. She's trialled well at the Sunshine Coast and won her only start this track/trip on the heavy. Has a low gate and the 2kg claim brings her into it. LADY WINDERMERE (6) resumed improved winning her Maiden at Eagle Farm and then was outgraded in a rich Quality at the Sunshine Coast. She has an awkward gate but is much better suited. MUSIC FEVER (9) is speedy and impressed first up when nudged out at the Gold Coast. She didn't finish it off there following but is better than that. Has been freshened and can improve into the money.
